This following talk has been mentioned several times, but just now I got aware of its importance:<br>
[Mon May 14 21:51:34 2001] You say, 'What has bertoxxulous released on Norrath?'<br>
[Mon May 14 21:51:34 2001] Roesager Thusten says 'Bertoxxulous is a vile creature who rules the Plane of Disease. His filthy followers are spreading their stain across all of Norrath. We fear they are already here in Qeynos. <br>
<br>
[Mon May 14 21:54:12 2001] You say, 'You speak of the Plane of Disease?'<br>
[Mon May 14 21:54:13 2001] Roesager Thusten says 'The Plaguebringers are followers of the disease lord, Bertoxxulous. We believe a sect of them now operates in Qeynos, but we need proof before we can act. <br>
<br>
[Mon May 14 21:54:25 2001] You say, 'What proof do you require?'<br>
[Mon May 14 21:54:25 2001] Roesager Thusten says 'Someone reported seeing a Plaguebringer roaming about in the hills near Qeynos. We have long suspected that their dark influence was spreading. I am searching for proof that they are now here in Qeynos. If you find anything, please bring it to me at the Temple of Life. <br>
<br>
So he mentiones the Plane of Disease!!<br>
This is the first sign all over Norrath that does namely mentoin this plane! Have you ever seen anyone in Norrath mention something that does absolutely not exist? I didn't.<br>
Also he asks for proof. Lets bring him this proof. We need to get Antonius Bayle listen to us. They need to get this proof so they can and WILL act! Maybe this can save Qeynos or at least wake them up. Qeynos itself seems to be still completely asleep. They do not know about hte dnager that comes from Kane, they do not know about the shrine. They need proof!<br>
<br>
S'raggs letter to Opal Darkbriar says that his forces are gathering. He is sending this to Opal Darkbriar. We need to find out more about Opal. What does he have to do with this? How would they and who would help them? S'raggs mentions the Lifers. These are obviously the Temple of Life's Followers. Do they know more? Did they find out? We must talk to them and share informations.<br>
<br>
<br>
The GM Event that Stimpie mentioned with the evil gnome (GNOME again!) sounds very special.<br>
The infos I miss in your reports is a) where did this happen and b) what happened after you got dispelled?<br>
I think you acted very good by NOT giving him the wand. (ooc: You may have lost a goodie from the GM for helping by doing so, brave soldier!) This for sure was what he did not expect. I would be really interested what happened after he dispelled you. <br>
<br>
Your other report Stimpie.- About this new person in Felwithe that told you he has be summoned to return to this world for some reason. This sounds like a very hot thing. Who in the wolrd would SUMMON people on this world (and who) if it would not be very important!<br>
Any additions are most welcome here too!<br>
<br>
<br>
There have been spottet many missionairies with notes, letters, cards, tactical maps...<br>
Looks like all Norrath is suddenly talkingt eachother. We need to stop these messengers! We need to get those letters and we need to read and see what is going on. So if you see any messenger or messenger to be. Stop them and find out whatever you can.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Please join the Council meeting next Friday (tomorrow), May 17th in South Karana. After you left the bridge from Northern Karana, turn left and the meeting will be on the hill. </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
It is critical that we now really get to a point where we KNOW what is going on, that we KNOW where and when and especially WHO will attack. We need to start really placing our forces and also, we need MORE volunteers to help to find out more.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> PLEASE do read this post carefully and THINK about all those details.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Please help me to make a picture out of this all. To see and to report and to find out is one thing. but to combine all those thousands of hints is the most important thing!<br>
<br>
